comments.body: [~accountid:636e6ef3c87c50433009887b]  : the name is changed and remittances turned on.

Hi [~accountid:613e6eaa1238e8007108f513] I called the CH to let him know the name change was completed and that he should have access to the remittances platform but during the troubleshooting he mentioned he wasn't receiving the link when sending the world ENVIO and we tried with the word MOVIMIENTO so that he could enter his portal but the option ENVIAR DINERO didn't displayed. I asked him to please send the number 5678 if this helps, because he confirmed he was sending the money from his number.
[~accountid:62b1de5fdcafd965c5ddeb7b]  I can look into this, but I also would like a new ticket for it since this is another request not related to the name change.

[https://www.howtogeek.com/771174/how-to-check-your-whatsapp-number/#:~:text=On%20the%20%E2%80%9CSettings%E2%80%9D%20page%2C,uses%20for%20your%20particular%20account.|https://www.howtogeek.com/771174/how-to-check-your-whatsapp-number/#:~:text=On%20the%20%E2%80%9CSettings%E2%80%9D%20page%2C,uses%20for%20your%20particular%20account.|smart-link]  please go through this with the CH
Any further communication on the message issues, let’s handle that in: [https://ganaz.atlassian.net/browse/GAN-5761|https://ganaz.atlassian.net/browse/GAN-5761|smart-link]
